{"type": "article", "id": 34137, "title": "豆子拼配那么多，怎么讲好咖啡的故事？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-11-04T23:47:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 123, "name": "咖啡"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 33194, "name": "AKU"}, {"id": 34630, "name": "Noem9 Studio"}, {"id": 34631, "name": "Voice Design"}, {"id": 34632, "name": "Kokomo"}, {"id": 20036, "name": "Kind"}, {"id": 20697, "name": "Ozo"}, {"id": 30113, "name": "Good Apples"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 416, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161105124811KSczJDhroT6YC7mx.png", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">无论里面装的是豆子还是粉末，咖啡包装的核心终归还是围绕着产地、风味在内的专业概念展开的。对于并不是非常了解相关知识的消费者来说，那些能将信息简化后更加生动活泼地表现出来的包装更能激发购买的欲望。我们此前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29475.html\">反常规咖啡包装</a>就是一次相当大胆的尝试，本周的主题就是那些想换种方式让你了解自己在喝什么的创意。</p><p>          </p><h3>EOS by Noem9 Studio</h3><p>如何用最简单的方式表现出咖啡的风味？西班牙 <a href=\"http://www.noem9studio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Noem9 Studio</a> 选择了被人们视为麻烦存在的咖啡渍，将概念品牌 EOS 的三种口味以一种直观的方式呈现出由清淡到浓郁之间的变化，简洁又很讨巧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175712YcKLRltfsWmQbh4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611041757110c6AfqEGzurLmQJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175711QpqhoYlZvznyI3TF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175711r9qNWyHog2pG7sMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Coffinger by Jaeyong Lee</h3><p>          </p><p>泡咖啡免不了搅拌的动作，如果没有搅拌工具又该如何是好呢？设计师 Jaeyong Lee 为此带来了名为 Coffinger 的速溶咖啡包装，它的特别之处在于尾部为手指预留的空档，外包装上也相应地印有农民的手指。从顶端撕开包装倒出咖啡粉之后，将包装沿着手指翻过去，内部干净的一面就变成了咖啡勺，同时也不用再担心粉末没有倒干净的问题了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104215706Wzmk2H4ucPn7DZyO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.868333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104215707PGZhIEjvVC6Si9eL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jacu Coffee Roastery by Kind</h3><p>成立于 2011 年的 <a href=\"http://www.jacu.no/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jacu Coffee Roastery</a> 是挪威奥斯陆一家专营南美鸟屎咖啡（Jacu Bird Coffee）的咖啡馆，由 <a href=\"http://www.kindnorway.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kind</a> 负责<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/3194657/Jacu-Coffee-Roastery-Visual-identityBranding\" rel=\"nofollow\">形象设计</a>。为了突出咖啡的特点，出现在各类物品上的 logo 就是以类似咖啡豆和小鸟的粗字体呈现的。在店内现场购买的咖啡豆包装和袋子都采用了牛皮纸搭配版画印刷的形式，漂亮的蜡封更是起到了点睛的效果。（如果你喜欢 Kind 的设计风格，还可以看一看这款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26357.html\">烈酒包装</a>。）</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175757DsRlkmvdSX3qPy8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.601667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175727EBTpSeFdVNn1HftJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175727uXat8UoFp7OyMTsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.601667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175727zcD92spN0QIXwBhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175727nidtNf07E9bw42QR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175727EWfpnoVHvSCiBlm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rio Coffee by Voice Design</h3><p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.riocoffee.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rio Coffee</a> 来自澳大利亚，产地多元的豆子是它的一大招牌。为了突出原产地的特色，负责包装设计的 <a href=\"http://www.voicedesign.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Voice Design</a> 委托美国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.n8w.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nate Williams</a> 绘制了四组色彩鲜艳的插画。Williams 那极具个性的画风赋予包装很强的存在感，生动地呈现出了各地的风土人情，而咖啡的背景故事则安排在了盒子的另一侧，排版看起来也相当精简有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180054CTiVK3hkjY92B0eL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180054LGzyTcHxapAsZrh9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180054Cm34tasVOWHfYFL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180054VHL5IC9eFyKWlnbp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180054LeN6CzSAlfRInkpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>OZO Coffee by Good Apples</h3><p>如果一个咖啡品牌有 30 种以上的拼配组合，要清楚地分辨它们可不是件容易的事。<a href=\"http://goodapples.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Good Apples</a> 为美国咖啡公司 <a href=\"https://ozocoffee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OZO</a> 出的主意相当有趣：设计师们不仅创作了 50 多个各具特色的象形文字，还设立了对应的排版规则。在这个系统的帮助下，顾客在挑选的过程中也被普及了每一款咖啡的背景资料。由于组合实在是有点多，设计师们最后又将它们按照口味分为三种大类，对应蓝绿红三色，让包装显得更加生动活泼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175847bfIkiJpOhCKH2v5R.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.417000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611041758483UWTjgIaocQ4LXiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810440\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175848SCGOKRnlLqd67X5c.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.719000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175849fHw3mtQoKZdIe8xk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985989\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175848hlzimcEy17vCLjO2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104175848d4VaR9UubCnKirNk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kokomo Coffee by AKU</h3><p>爱沙尼亚咖啡品牌 <a href=\"http://www.kokomo.ee/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kokomo</a> 成立于 2015 年，<a href=\"http://www.aku.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">AKU</a> 工作室和英国插画师 <a href=\"http://www.ryan-chapman.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ryan Chapman</a> 共同完成了这些烘培自非洲咖啡豆的产品包装。信息精简的标签和采用邮戳形式注明的烘培日期给人一种收到国际包裹的感觉，最上方还有 Chapman 为不同产地所绘制的卡通邮票。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180023pywFKHG4VfotuAJE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748571\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180023aX95Rzsb7WtZCLic.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180024VYIZoCgb4PelAqkD.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748571\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180023jwK3e6f2I1T08MHO.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104180024M6YQL9DsSzvT54EJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748571\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}